http://www.thehindu.com/news/cities/Hyderabad/Gift-yourself-an-international-trip/article14011195.ece

The Indian Railway Catering & Tourism Corporation (IRCTC) has announced fresh dates for its next international trip from Hyderabad to Malaysia and Singapore in March. Another trip to Thailand too is on the offer, but the starting point is Chennai, an official spokesperson said.The package duration to Malaysia and Singapore is five nights and six days (March 22 to 27) leaving Hyderabad on March 21 and returning on March 26. The package to Thailand is four nights and five days (March 3 to March 7) leaving Chennai on March 3 and returning on March 7.The tour package from Hyderabad to Malaysia/Singapore includes three nights in Kuala Lumpur and two nights’ stay in Singapore to cover the King’s Palace, National Mosque and museum, twin towers, parliament house etc. Sunway lagoon entertainment city built on the mountain, a resort and indoor theme park. Batu caves, Genting Highland indoor only, Putrajaya new city.For Singapore tour, one has to board the train and proceed to Singapore by road – Jurangbird park, drive round the city tour, garden by the bay civic district, Padang, cricket club, historic parliament house, supreme court, city hall, Merlion park, Thian Hock Keng Buddhist temple, Sentosa Island by scenic cable car ride and also Universal Studio with full one day trip.Fare for double or triple occupancy is Rs. 80,369; single occupancy – Rs. 94,261 and child without bed – Rs.56,671.The IRCTC will take care of the to and fro flight tickets, three-star category AC hotels, AC vehicle, English-speaking guide for the entire trip, IRCTC tour manager from Hyderabad Airport to Thailand and back to Hyderabad, lunch and breakfast in Indian Restaurants with Continental breakfast for the entire trip. Visa charges, entry fees and insurance are included in the package. There will not be any hidden charges to the tourists and package cost is inclusive of all taxes. For further details, contact Hyderabad - 040-277012407, 23800580, 9701360605/609/647/671/701/729. Vijayawada - 08662572280, 9701360620, Tirupati - 0877-2222010.The tour package from Chennai to Thailand and back is of three nights and four days including two nights’ stay in Pattaya and one night stay in Bangkok.For further details, contact: Vijayawada-0866-2572280, 9701360632, Tirupati-0877-2222010, 9701360689, 9701360620.